metadata.description:
## Staplehead Ghouliani  
  
**Damp flesh unravels ceaselessly.**  
**Endless rain can't hide the foul odor of the small man in the nice suit.**  
**A cenobite? Worse; a lawyer.** 
  
*Stable diffusion and an unstable mind summon Ghouliani II #2 from the deepest depths of depravity.*  
     
Built from GHOULIANI #2 : https://opensea.io/assets/matic/0xc1a903b7163b72036b0a0e5a5375293cb15ad727/2/
